thread.title: George W. Bush cheers on SMU, gets on Jumbotron
thread.title_full: George W. Bush cheers on SMU, gets on Jumbotron

author: Sara Harris (sharris@sportingnews.com)
title: George W. Bush cheers on SMU, gets on Jumbotron
text:
23pm  23pm EST Former President George W. Bush had a great time supporting No. 25 SMU during the Mustangs' 60-51 win over No. 11 Cincinnati on Sunday. George W. Bush (Getty Images) 
Updated at 7:23  23 p.m. ET 
George W. Bush had a great time supporting No. 25 SMU during the Mustangs' 60-51 win over No. 11 Cincinnati on Sunday. 
The 43rd president of the United States sat courtside at the game and eventually ended up on the arena's Jumbotron.
